Package: taxminer
Title: Taxonomic annotations - BLAST alignment and text-mining based filtration in R 
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Schahzad Saqib [aut, cre] (ORCID = https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0844-2124)
Maintainer: Schahzad Saqib <schahzad.saqib@helsinki.fi>
Description: Facilitates customized BLAST based taxonomic annotations and uses the rentrez package https://github.com/ropensci/rentrez to communicate with NCBI databases to extract information based on accession IDs. This information attaches ecosystem specificity to each annotation hit, which is used as a filtration criteria to obtain the most probablistic taxonomic annotations. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
